  "text": "MLST. MLST was performed as previously described [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . In brief, the partial sequences of eight genetic loci, including 16S rRNA-DNA, batR, ftsZ, gltA, groEL, nlpD, ribC and rpoB, were analysed. The PCR products were purified and sequenced on both strands with an ABI 3730 XL apparatus (AGOWA, DNA sequencing service, Berlin, Germany). The DNA sequences were analysed by using the DNASTAR Lasergene. Alleles and sequence types (STs) were assigned in accordance with the published data [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
